        image="/images/custom-shirts/top5pct-banner-custom-apparel-custom-shirts-custom-hoodies-custom-caps.jpg"
        alt="Custom branded drink coasters for restaurants and businesses in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Your Brand on Every Table"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Custom branded drink coasters put your logo in front of every person who sits down at a table in your space. For restaurants, bars, coffee shops, and offices throughout Joliet and Will County, coasters are a quiet but persistent brand touchpoint that guests interact with every time they set down a drink, and many establishments pair their branded coasters with <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">branded mugs</a> for a complete drinkware identity that carries the same logo from the shelf to the table. A well-designed custom coaster also functions as a conversation piece that guests notice and remember, making it a surprisingly effective branding tool for businesses that serve people in a seated environment, and for complete table branding that goes beyond coasters our <a href="/signs/table-signs/table-cloths" class="link-notification">custom table cloths</a> carry your logo across the entire table surface.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">We produce custom coasters in ceramic, neoprene, and hardboard materials with full-color printing that covers the entire surface. Ceramic coasters have a glossy finished look with a cork backing and are popular for corporate gifts and upscale branded merchandise. Neoprene coasters are soft, grippy, and moisture-resistant, making them ideal for bars and restaurants, and for complete restaurant table branding our <a href="/signs/table-signs/table-cloths" class="link-notification">custom table cloths</a> carry your logo across the entire table surface. Hardboard coasters are a durable, eco-friendly option with a natural wood-like appearance and excellent print quality.</p>
        <p>Custom coasters are also a popular item for corporate gift sets, event giveaways, wedding favors, and holiday gift packages. We have no minimums and can produce small personal orders as well as large commercial quantities. Call us at (815) 349 8600 to discuss your custom coaster order today.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/custom-shirts/top5pct-custom-embroidery-shops-near-me-joliet.jpg"
        alt="Custom coaster materials and branded drinkware accessories for businesses in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Ceramic, Neoprene, and Hardboard Options"
        imagePosition="right"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Selecting the right coaster material depends on your application and the impression you want your branded coaster to make. Ceramic coasters project a premium, upscale quality that makes them ideal for executive gift sets, client appreciation packages, and hospitality establishments that position themselves in the upper tier of their market, and for a complete corporate gift set that pairs with ceramic coasters our <a href="/promotional-items/mugs" class="link-notification">branded mugs</a> carry the same logo for a full drinkware package. The glossy surface of a ceramic coaster allows for rich, photographic-quality printing that makes logo artwork and full-color designs look exceptional, and for clients whose logo needs a professional update before printing our <a href="/design-services/logo-design" class="link-notification">logo design</a> team creates clean vector artwork specifically optimized for small-format, high-resolution applications like coasters and mugs.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Neoprene coasters are the workhorses of the bar and restaurant world. They are durable, easy to clean, and the rubber-like surface provides excellent grip that prevents glasses from sliding. They absorb condensation effectively and can withstand the volume of use that comes with a busy service environment. Neoprene is the preferred material for restaurants and bars throughout Joliet and Will County that want branded coasters that hold up through a busy shift without looking worn or degraded, and many bar and restaurant owners bundle their coaster orders with <a href="/promotional-items/can-koozies" class="link-notification">custom can koozies</a> for a complete branded drinkware experience.</p>
        <p>Hardboard coasters offer a middle ground, they have the premium appearance of ceramic without the brittleness, and they have the durability of neoprene without the rubbery aesthetic. They are especially popular for corporate branded gift sets and organizations looking for a distinctive branded coaster that does not look or feel like a standard promotional item. Call us at (815) 349 8600 to discuss which material is right for your custom coaster project.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

